they'll still sign with you?

589
00:30:48,688 --> 00:30:51,570
What's important now? It's all about
cost reduction and efficiency now.

590
00:30:51,660 --> 00:30:53,460
Money has to be spent where it matters.

591
00:30:53,820 --> 00:30:54,180
Well,

592
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:55,422
my Shattered Six States

593
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:57,460
is much better than your mess,

594
00:30:57,460 --> 00:30:58,180
don't you think?

595
00:30:58,355 --> 00:30:59,420
Your Shattered Six States

596
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:00,780
isn't even halfway done yet.

597
00:31:01,488 --> 00:31:02,720
Will it fall apart at the end?

598
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:03,780
Who knows?

599
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:05,100
Impossible.

600
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:07,580
Because it's written by me, He Han.

601
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:42,220
Ling Yikai,

602
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:45,820
