603
00:31:47,580 --> 00:31:48,555
Have you decided?

604
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:51,300
Friendship or the market?

605
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:52,820
Can I choose love?

606
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:56,940
That's not an option.

607
00:31:57,220 --> 00:31:58,020
I added it myself.

608
00:31:58,820 --> 00:32:00,340
If we were in a relationship,

609
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:01,977
then if you went out
to start a business,

610
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,244
I would support you.

611
00:32:03,980 --> 00:32:05,911
I need to give Lin Zhanqiao
a reason to leave

612
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,260
and also give myself one.

613
00:32:10,622 --> 00:32:11,955
Let me think about it.

614
00:32:13,355 --> 00:32:15,155
So, are we still having dinner?

615
00:32:15,220 --> 00:32:15,700
No appetite.

616
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:27,100
(Mengtong Internet Cafe)

617
00:32:27,100 --> 00:32:28,220
- One more bowl.
- Coming right up.

618
00:32:28,220 --> 00:32:29,180
Okay, thank you, ma'am.

619
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:10,540
Here.

620
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:11,740
Here.

621
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:19,660
Dear friends,

622
00:33:19,888 --> 00:33:22,155
