623
00:33:22,222 --> 00:33:24,266
to the author
of Shattered Six States, He Han.

624
00:33:38,220 --> 00:33:39,940
Alright, for today's signing ceremony,

625
00:33:40,020 --> 00:33:41,140
as you can all see,

626
00:33:41,288 --> 00:33:43,355
the author
of Shattered Six States, He Han,

627
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,580
has come in person

628
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:47,700
to attend
the film adaptation licensing ceremony

629
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:49,860
for the novel Shattered Six States.

630
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:50,860
As we all know,

631
00:33:50,860 --> 00:33:52,540
this is He Han's second work this year

632
00:33:52,540 --> 00:33:54,540
to be adapted for the screen.

633
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:56,980
(Texing Video)
From 2020 until now,

634
00:33:57,180 --> 00:33:58,740
(So excited!)
He Han's intellectual property can be

635
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:01,100
(So handsome!)
said to guarantee blockbuster success.

636
00:34:01,340 --> 00:34:03,340
(Among the top five)

637
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:05,380
(costume dramas in platform viewership,)

638
00:34:05,380 --> 00:34:06,500
(three of them)

639
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:09,020
(are adapted from He Han's novels.)

640
00:34:09,180 --> 00:34:10,620
(So from the time He Han)

641
00:34:10,900 --> 00:34:12,700
(began writing Shattered Six States,)

642
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:14,822
(we decided)

643
00:34:14,911 --> 00:34:16,466
at all costs

644
00:34:16,860 --> 00:34:17,780
