645
00:34:17,860 --> 00:34:19,860
Can you reveal roughly
how much the rights fee is?

646
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:20,700
(Congratulations!)

647
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:21,820
(That's incredible!)

648
00:34:21,820 --> 00:34:22,540
Sky-high price.

649
00:34:23,180 --> 00:34:24,820
(Alright, the signing ceremony)

650
00:34:25,140 --> 00:34:26,420
(officially begins now.)

651
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:36,220
Please sign the agreement.

652
00:34:40,444 --> 00:34:41,711
Let's move signings

653
00:34:41,733 --> 00:34:42,580
to the afternoon next time.

654
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:44,300
It's too early.
I didn't even dare sleep.

655
00:34:47,180 --> 00:34:50,780
(Authorized Signatory He Han)

656
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:53,700
Mr. He Han,

657
00:34:53,980 --> 00:34:55,100
