659
00:34:56,733 --> 00:34:57,540
It's not that much.

660
00:34:57,540 --> 00:34:58,820
Isn't it just 10,000 words a day?

661
00:34:58,820 --> 00:34:59,977
What is there to keep up?

662
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:01,380
In your opinion,

663
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:03,020
