687
00:36:13,980 --> 00:36:15,460
We still have many top authors.

688
00:36:15,660 --> 00:36:16,977
Recently, we've also spent money

689
00:36:17,060 --> 00:36:18,380
to sign many new authors.

690
00:36:18,580 --> 00:36:19,460
With so many people,

691
00:36:19,580 --> 00:36:21,955
I don't believe
that not one of them can beat He Han.

692
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:23,660
I don't think he's untouchable.

693
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:27,420
If in the time ahead,

694
00:36:27,420 --> 00:36:29,133
he still stays number one
on the rankings

695
00:36:29,180 --> 00:36:30,380
and never drops,

696
00:36:30,380 --> 00:36:32,580
then it only proves
our authors lack ability,

697
00:36:32,580 --> 00:36:34,955
our editors lack ability,
and Chenxing lacks ability.

698
00:36:36,460 --> 00:36:38,900
I completely agree
with what was just said.

699
00:36:39,540 --> 00:36:41,340
We surely have strong authors.

700
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:44,100
He Han may be number one,

701
00:36:44,300 --> 00:36:45,780
but within the top 20,

702
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:47,300
we still hold two spots.

703
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:49,220
Also, this month,

704
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:50,220
we sold two more

705
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:52,540
film rights at good prices.

706
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:53,740
The fact is,

707
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:55,780
our entire company's
annual copyright revenue

708
00:36:55,900 --> 00:36:57,100
