709
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:59,444
what He Han signed this morning
for Shattered Six States.

710
00:36:59,466 --> 00:37:01,200
And Shattered Six States
is only partially updated.

711
00:37:01,288 --> 00:37:03,000
That's why we need you to step up.

712
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:04,340
What content do you have

713
00:37:04,340 --> 00:37:06,244
that could compete
with Shattered Six States?

714
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,088
We'll focus on them.

715
00:37:07,100 --> 00:37:08,290
At the End of Yue Lu Lights.

716
00:37:08,290 --> 00:37:09,700
You're bringing that up again.

717
00:37:13,340 --> 00:37:14,500
Give me some other names.

718
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:15,500
What about

719
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:17,220
those so-called "big shots"

720
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:18,700
you all treat so carefully

721
00:37:18,700 --> 00:37:19,620
