722
00:37:20,740 --> 00:37:22,180
What progress have they made now?

723
00:37:22,244 --> 00:37:23,900
If you can beat your opponents,
you're a master.

724
00:37:23,900 --> 00:37:25,660
If you can beat He Han, you're a legend.

725
00:37:25,860 --> 00:37:26,780
Otherwise, don't keep

726
00:37:26,780 --> 00:37:28,733
talking to me about
special treatment for legends!

727
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:33,940
Fragile.

728
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:36,380
Tell me about the new authors first.

729
00:37:39,660 --> 00:37:41,300
You've already met the six new ones.

730
00:37:41,300 --> 00:37:43,066
They're competing with Homeward Fields.

731
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:43,900
And these

732
00:37:44,377 --> 00:37:46,100
are the promising
new authors I've shortlisted

733
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:47,540
over the past few months,

734
00:37:47,540 --> 00:37:49,020
their project summaries, and data.

735
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:52,140
For the top 20,

736
00:37:52,377 --> 00:37:53,940
get their chapters one,
twenty, and eighty

737
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:54,740
for me now.

738
00:37:54,933 --> 00:37:56,340
The top ten can all be interviewed.

739
00:37:56,350 --> 00:37:57,900
If any of them fit,
move forward immediately.

740
00:37:57,900 --> 00:37:58,260
Alright.

741
00:37:59,340 --> 00:37:59,900
Mr. He Han.

742
00:38:00,780 --> 00:38:01,420
Mr. He Han.

743
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:03,220
There's a meeting going on inside.

744
00:38:03,420 --> 00:38:04,060
Let it.

745
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:06,660
♪Never♪

746
00:38:11,340 --> 00:38:12,460
♪Never Stop♪

747
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:17,860
♪Never Stop♪

748
00:38:22,044 --> 00:38:23,540
♪Watch my words come alive in bloom♪

749
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:24,980
♪Unleash six states in a chain of blows♪

750
00:38:24,980 --> 00:38:26,140
♪See a genius born to soar♪

751
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:27,700
♪Rising high where the wide skies glow♪

752
00:38:27,700 --> 00:38:28,820
♪If you can catch my shadow♪

753
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:30,380
♪You can cross the world and roam free♪

754
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:31,540
♪Your next stop in your heart♪

755
00:38:31,540 --> 00:38:33,100
♪Must be me at the top♪

756
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:35,220
♪Neon lights glaring bright♪

757
00:38:35,220 --> 00:38:36,111
Congratulations.

758
00:38:36,377 --> 00:38:38,020
Another project sold at a high price.

759
00:38:38,460 --> 00:38:39,100
Two.

760
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:40,580
The next one is already theirs too,

761
00:38:40,820 --> 00:38:42,580
just not officially announced yet.

762
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:44,340
What's it called?

763
00:38:45,355 --> 00:38:46,288
Haven't decided.

764
00:38:46,740 --> 00:38:48,740
So basically, with your name,

765
00:38:49,060 --> 00:38:50,620
plus Dai Shan's support,

766
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:52,010
and Mr. Fan backing it,

767
00:38:52,010 --> 00:38:53,400
they will take whatever you write?

768
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:55,220
And it's all paid upfront.

769
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:57,180
She knows it.

770
00:38:57,180 --> 00:38:58,800
She's a veteran editor of ten years.

771
00:39:01,260 --> 00:39:01,980
New girlfriend?

772
00:39:03,260 --> 00:39:03,820
This is Mimi.

773
00:39:03,888 --> 00:39:05,300
She's also an online fiction author.

774
00:39:05,340 --> 00:39:06,540
This is my ex, Lin Zhanqiao.

775
00:39:06,820 --> 00:39:08,540
Top promoter, and top editor.

776
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:09,450
Get to know each other.

777
00:39:09,450 --> 00:39:11,340
If she signs you, your future is set.

778
00:39:11,580 --> 00:39:12,400
I don't want that.

779
00:39:12,977 --> 00:39:14,266
I only want to sign with you.

780
00:39:16,940 --> 00:39:18,820
See, fate works in unexpected ways

781
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:19,340
